<div class="overflow-x-auto contain-inline-size"><table data-start="640" data-end="1315" node="[object Object]"><thead data-start="640" data-end="687"><tr data-start="640" data-end="687"><th data-start="640" data-end="672">Feature</th><th data-start="672" data-end="687">Description</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="735" data-end="1315"><tr data-start="735" data-end="846"><td>🔐 JWT Authentication</td><td>Uses <code data-start="773" data-end="804">Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;</code> in header to access secured n8n webhook</td></tr><tr data-start="847" data-end="929"><td>👤 Login System</td><td>Secure login using encrypted (bcrypt) passwords</td></tr><tr data-start="930" data-end="1020"><td>🧾 Equipment Entry Form</td><td>Allows logged-in users to submit equipment data to n8n</td></tr><tr data-start="1021" data-end="1102"><td>🛠 Admin Panel</td><td>Add/Delete users, reset passwords (admin-only)</td></tr><tr data-start="1103" data-end="1202"><td>🆕 First-Time Admin Setup</td><td>Automatically prompts admin to set up first user if none exists</td></tr><tr data-start="1203" data-end="1315"><td>🗂 No External DB</td><td>All users stored in memory or in <code data-start="1270" data-end="1282">users.json</code> (optionally in <code data-start="1298" data-end="1312">localStorage</code>)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
