<div class="overflow-x-auto contain-inline-size"><table data-start="2491" data-end="2806" node="[object Object]"><thead data-start="2491" data-end="2508"><tr data-start="2491" data-end="2508"><th data-start="2491" data-end="2498">Step</th><th data-start="2498" data-end="2508">Action</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="2527" data-end="2806"><tr data-start="2527" data-end="2598"><td>1</td><td>App checks if <code data-start="2550" data-end="2562">users.json</code> is empty or lacks an "admin" user</td></tr><tr data-start="2599" data-end="2635"><td>2</td><td>Redirects to <code data-start="2621" data-end="2633">setup.html</code></td></tr><tr data-start="2636" data-end="2677"><td>3</td><td>Admin enters username/password</td></tr><tr data-start="2678" data-end="2724"><td>4</td><td>Password is hashed using <code data-start="2712" data-end="2722">bcryptjs</code></td></tr><tr data-start="2725" data-end="2772"><td>5</td><td>User is saved with <code data-start="2753" data-end="2770">"role": "admin"</code></td></tr><tr data-start="2773" data-end="2806"><td>6</td><td>Redirect to login page</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
